    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood from the species Acacia melanoxylon, reddish brown to black in color and prized for attractive grain, appearing similar to rosewood. The strong, elastic, hardwood is used for furniture, walking sticks, and tool handles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
